                        <th height="1433" align="left" class="f-left"><div align="left" id="content-in">
                          <p>AudioWire is a software that can play a majority of audio formats such as WAV, MIDI, MP3, XMA, OGG, and more!<br />
                          The project is available on multiple operating systems (Windows 7 &amp; 8, Mac osX 10.6 and later, and linux).</p>
                          <p>The integrate artificial intelligence is able to find out what the users likes and dislikes, on moods, etc. Based on this and on information given by the server, the software will create &quot;Smart Playlists&quot;.<br />
                          These &quot;Smart Playlists&quot; will therefore suit the music<em><img src="/assets/aw_screen.jpg" alt="" width="251" height="197" id="Screenshot" align="right" /></em>al tastes of the user, and will be sharable with other users.</p>
                          <p>The software will also allow playback of music on multiple computers simultaneously, either on a local area network, or via Internet.<br />
                            Think of it like this, you're having a party and you're in need of more than one audio output. All you need to do is grab a couple of computers (or more) and start our software. With a little magic, the computers will play the same music at the same time.</p>
                          <p>AudioWire also has more &quot;social&quot; features. The chat will let you communicate with friends while listening<br />
                            and sharing your favourite songs. <br />
                            Of course you will be able to Share your playlists with your friends and to listen to theirs.<br />
                            Finally, you'll find some more &quot;classic&quot; features such as &quot;visualizer&quot; or podcast/radio player and an advanced music library management.</p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p><em>Here's the more detailed list of the features :</em></p>
                          <p><span class="title">* Basic Audio Player</span> Features :<br />
                            <span class="ul-style01"><code>- Library Manager<br />
                            - Playlist creator<br />
                            - Visualizer<br />
                          - etc.</code></span></p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p>* &quot;Smart&quot; Playlist<br />
                            <code>This will play a list of songs you may enjoy based on :<br />
                            - Songs that you've listened to<br />
                            - Your mood (Select your mood and the software will establish a playlist based on it)<br />
                          - Selected songs (Select a couple or more songs and the algorithm will find similar songs in your library)</code></p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p>* Network Sync<br />
                            <code>Ever wanted to have more than one computer in your home playing the same tune ?<br />
                            This feature will allow you to synchronise playback over multiple computers in your home network.<br />
                            Oh, and guess what ?! It also allows you to listen to songs with friends over the internet!</code></p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p>* Social features<br />
                            <code>- Share your playlists and &quot;Smart&quot; playlists with friends<br />
                            - Chat with your friends while listening to music (see Network Sync)<br />
                            - File sharing<br />
                            - Cross-user music streaming</code></p>
                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <p>** And remember, our software will be available on Windows, Mac &amp; Linux!</p>
